It looks like you opened the help menu and before the show menu event was 
processed the workbench got closed and the menu got disposed.
Near impossible to reproduce. I will talk to SN since I think we should not get 
the event at that point.

Moving to SWT. I think we should not get an show/hide event if the menu is 
disposed. KeyBindingMenu is the hidden menu for the keybinding.

Eduardo and Lynne, I haven't heard of this one for a while.  Please reopen if 
it happens again.  Thanks.
